    "image_with_text_ArDE7Y": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_AKA74Q": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Molly's Love of Gardens"
          }
        },
        "text_j3jMar": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In the world of Molly Mahon, gardens are an endless source of inspiration.</p><p>Her hand block printed textiles echo their language - layered florals, natural rhythm, and a sense of joyful imperfection. Like a garden left to grow with intention but not control, the work feels alive, abundant, and constantly evolving.</p>",
